## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies

| Tool | Version | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| Python | 3.x | Core language |
| Pandas | 1.x+ | Data preprocessing & feature engineering |
| NumPy | Latest | Bootstrap sampling & numerical operations |
| Scikit-learn | Latest | Linear Regression, train/test split, RMSE |
| Matplotlib | Latest | Profit distribution visualizations |
| Jupyter Notebook | Latest | Analysis environment |

**Techniques used:**
- Linear Regression (reserve volume prediction)
- Bootstrap Sampling (profit simulation, 1,000 iterations)
- Confidence Interval Estimation
- Risk/Loss Probability Calculation

