## ⚙️ Setup & Deployment

**Requirements:**
```
python >= 3.8
pandas >= 1.3.0
numpy >= 1.21.0
scikit-learn >= 0.24.0
matplotlib >= 3.4.0
jupyter >= 1.0.0
```

**To run locally:**
```bash
# 1. Clone this repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/oilygiant-well-selection.git

# 2. Navigate into the project folder
cd oilygiant-well-selection

# 3. Install dependencies
pip install pandas numpy scikit-learn matplotlib jupyter

# 4. Launch the notebook
jupyter notebook oil_well_selection.ipynb
```

